A 17-year-old youth has been arrested for allegedly killing his girlfriend, and is due to appear at the Motetema Magistrate s Court today.The incident happened yesterday in Motetema near Groblersdal in Limpopo. It is reported that the body of the 15-year-old was found by a passer-by near the Tafelkop Mountain with multiple injuries.Police spokesperson Moatshe Ngoepe confirmed today that a suspect had been arrested and is in custody charged with murder.Ngoepe said although circumstances surrounding her death were not clear, but there were allegations that the suspect tried to force the deceased to abort a pregnancy.TNA Reporter 